        <p>Drexel’s School of Biomedical Engineering, Science and Health Systems was established almost 60 years ago, with a foundation of excellent basic research that informs the school’s current teaching, translational research, and service activities, all in the pursuit of achieving clinical and industrial relevance, thus creating the educational experiences that prepare its students for emerging biomedical challenges. </p>
